Sync Observations

Process (since this is so complex):
1. FOR EACH OBSERVATION
    1.1 Archive the Observation
    1.2 Merge in the Changes
    1.3 Translate the Observation Details
    1.4 PERFORM SYNC MATCH AND UPDATE WHERE NECESSARY (TALK TO TRENT)
    1.5 After all Detail records are successfully stored, Update Observation so Observation.definition contains the serialized array of Details
2. Get all observation records for this user that have changed since the sync date

Request to render a report. To get rendered files, use getReportStageFile()
Example HTML flow:
1. Request /Report/Render/1247/default
